mport raw voltage signals from matlab file

pre_import_matlab.Rd

mport raw voltage signals from matlab file

pre_import_matlab(subject_code, project_name, block_num, chl,
  name = "analogTraces")

Arguments

subject_code

subject code
project_name

project name
block_num

which block of signals will be looked into?
chl

integer, channel number
name

which matlab variable to look at, default is "analogTraces"

Value

raw signal
